Trip planner

------Please find a video demo of this app at : 
      https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=biFU1RKtGPE&feature=youtu.be

------ Registration

User can signup/login in the following ways:

1. Email, Username
2. Google Authentication

------ App Functionalities


- Every user can send request to other user and make friends.

- Friends/Pending requests are shown in a separate section

- Friends can plan trips.

- Every trip has a chat room.

- User can delete messages on his side without affecting the experience for other users in the discussion

- Images can be sent through chat room

- User can add locations to the trip

- All the locations are shown in a map embedded into the map.

- Map shows the round trip from current location of the user covering all the locations added to the trip




-------- Technologies used

Used following to complete the app successfully:

Google Maps Api
Google Authentication 
Firebase Database
Firebase Storage
RecyclerView
CardView
Picasso (loading images asynchronously)





